reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These silicone utensils leave nothing to be critiqued. They boast an appealing appearance, a delightful tactile experience, remarkable heat resistance, and impressive durability. No rips, cracks, seams, or blemishes were evident, contributing to their overall quality. However, a minor critique, which applies to most silicone utensils, is the wish for sturdier tips. While they excel in many tasks, scraping the bottom of a pan or effectively lifting/flipping food may require additional assistance from plastic or wooden utensils.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars GREAT VALUE & pretty colors!
reviews.reviewText: Love the set! Virtually unbeatable price, nice variety, and the multicolors make kitchen work fun! I found them to be very durable-- they held up on both the stovetop and in the dishwasher with no melting or dent marks. Packaged nicely; each spatula came individually wrapped in the box.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Pure frustration took me on a journey to find my idea of the perfect spatula. . .and I succeeded! This set has performed the rigors of homemade smoothies, chili, apple butter, pear chutney, quiche, mayo, refried beans, blueberry muffins, sauces, . . .and more, with stellar results. But here lays the satisfaction: each piece is constructed in one part. No more separate handles to clean or loose attachment heads to deal with resulting in easy clean up.. That alone is worth five stars. However, this set is BPA free, heat resistant and the stickiness of ingredients slide off. This product was purchased in August 2023 and submitting review 2 months later. Recommendation: High
